2012;;Now Is Good;;British;;Director: Ol Parker;;Director: Ol ParkerCast: Dakota Fanning, Jeremy Irvine, Paddy Considine, Olivia Williams, Kaya Scodelario;;unknown;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Now_Is_Good;;Tessa, a teen with terminal acute lymphoblastic leukemia, tries to complete a bucket list of things to do before her impending death. Her friend Zoey helps her. Tessa's mother is supportive though her father appears to be in denial, and her brother Cal finds his emotions about the situation varying wildly. Tessa falls for her neighbor Adam, who is caring for his sickly widowed mother.